flowchart TD
  A[Developer adds or edits source] --> B[Run npm run lint]
  B --> C[git ls-files cached plus untracked non-ignored files]
  C --> D[Include roots and code extensions]
  D --> E[Exclude generated dependency build coverage and artifact paths]
  E --> F[Read text files and skip binary files safely]
  F --> G[Whitespace tab and readability checks]
  G --> H[Apply validated readability allowlist]
  H --> I{Failures?}
  I -- Yes --> J[Print rule path line and remediation summary]
  I -- No --> K[Print scanned count allowlisted count and duration]
  J --> L[Developer fixes source or documents a valid exception]
  L --> B
